  <p>To ask the Scottish Executive <a name="QuestionText">what the timetable is for the appointment of the new chief executive of VisitScotland.</a></p>

</ques>


<reply id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2001-07-23.S1W-16721.r0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80131" speakername="Ms Wendy Alexander" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-01/wa0723.htm#QuestionText">

  <p>The appointment of the new chief executive was announced on 16 July 2001.</p>

</reply>
